WEBVTT

00:00.750 --> 00:03.915
That man! He has stirred up the mob,
he has set them on a rampage!

00:03.917 --> 00:05.892
Well, what did you expect,
when you closed a working mine?

00:05.894 --> 00:08.838
Have a care.
You may be taken at your word.

00:08.840 --> 00:11.158
This is not London.
Do you suppose there are spies here?

00:11.160 --> 00:13.798
Dear God, the twisted quirk of fate
that gives the girl I love

00:13.800 --> 00:15.758
-to the man I loathe.
-George?

00:15.760 --> 00:16.998
If that is what you desire.

00:17.000 --> 00:19.358
I do not believe
I will feel desire ever again.

00:19.360 --> 00:22.158
Is it really so terrible?
The thought of a child?

00:22.160 --> 00:24.718
No. But the loss is.

00:24.720 --> 00:26.958
Can a mother truly forget
a son she birthed?

00:26.960 --> 00:29.278
I am your mistress no longer, Tess.

00:29.280 --> 00:30.840
Pack your things and go.

